            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "You can see the filetypes it's loaded for here: https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/blob/9141be4c1332afc83bdf1b0278dbb030f75ff8e3/lsp/angularls.lua#L82\n\nBut, that config is pretty flawed: its logic happens at module-load time. Instead it should define a `reuse_client` handler, and/or `root_dir`.\n\nThat's up to you or other angular users. We don't support these configs, you need to improve them if you use them.\n\n(And send improvements here :)",
